{"tid":1459963,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[勸世文]天埼講過：愈憤怒愈要冷靜","createTime":"2019-08-13T00:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:58:00.000Z","uid":245965,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"db988eddc3aa8a428b58e24719081885a6bfdd0a","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:14:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">琴日結果成唔成功 其實冇人知<br />\n我地留比未來既歷史去判斷</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而係大量p牌仔/阿蛇係到帶風向<br />\n然後大量分化撚同道歉撚上撚哂線<br />\n<br />\n講左十萬次現場錫春袋都唔撚割<br />\n衰左咪聽日再黎囉<br />\n走左又冇咩損失<br />\n<br />\n而家係講緊係機場走唔撚到真係困獸鬥<br />\n而家班狗咁撚癲冇哂人性<br />\n又玩扮示威者衝突 人地都話到明示威者唔破壞唔出手 背後意思咪搵幾隻狗換黑杉搞破壞就出師有名<br />\n到時班手足比人捉撚哂又傷撚哂 <br />\n<br />\n手足唔係你地既軍隊 亦唔係你地既奴隸 大家係有共同信念先互相尊重出黎一齊抗爭 唔該你要尊重每個人既諗法 呢個亦係現場判斷點都唔割既理由<br />\n<br />\n然後最厲害有人話我咁諗係淆底 <br />\n咁怕狗隻唔駛成功乜乜77 <br />\n仲有唔少人自己打擊自己<br />\n係咁自己話自己柒左<br />\n又道撚哂歉話自己係散水撚<br />\n<br />\n我想講從來都唔係怕犧牲<br />\n係怕<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無意義既犧牲</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n係呀留守係會集中到焦點呀 咪比班狗慢慢各個擊破 拉左一個就少一個 到時咪冇撚哂人囉 同雨革一樣繼續死守啦 繼續相信留係到就會成功啦<br />\n<br />\n現場資訊如此混亂 擇日再戰唔係逃兵 唔係逃避 要笑我地散水撚就由佢笑 笑到最後既先係贏家 而家一日未贏就不停分化互屌<br />\n<br />\n政府都唔知幾撚開心<br />\n<br />\n道歉果d先最撚好笑<br />\n唔知佢真心 定想扮慘分化<br />\n一係就係心態唔好 覺得出黎一定要勇武 冇衝到就覺得出黎哂左 而家去玩咩屌你老味<br />\n<br />\n又有義士/扮義士係到係咁話好嬲今日輸哂 <br />\n又話你地對得住女義士咩好撚失望 之餘似類 係到嘗試分化 結果真係好撚多人信 真係笑撚死我<br />\n我屌佢地分化屌返我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女義士已經犧牲左隻眼 你覺得佢好返之後見到我地咁樣自我分裂好開心？仲要拎佢件事出黎互屌 政府就最撚開心啦<br />\n<br />\n唔該你地尊重返大家立場 咁多人諗法一定互相不同 但我地互相有共同目標 <br />\n<br />\n見到星期日既事我都好憤怒 咁都唔代表我要放棄冷靜去抗爭政府 你愈衝動愈會出錯 愈會提早令抗爭結束 <br />\n<br />\n請大家記住<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">現場錫春袋都唔撚割<br />\n現場錫春袋都唔撚割<br />\n現場錫春袋都唔撚割</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得係錯左既下次做好d<br />\n大家可以一齊反省<br />\n但唔可以互相指責 自我分裂<br />\n尤其係指責過左去既事<br />\n唔走都走左囉 一係返去一係撤退<br />\n屌住黎撤退過癮d？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry我見到大量分化撚 風向狗出現我都好唔冷靜打左咁多字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c58fccee45c1bc305c2c7d1528cb15b0c184c9","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:15:04.000Z","msg":"自推十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b69ff8ad6561b8dbb4ad7d9814781cbf408fa1","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:15:17.000Z","msg":"9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55592a8cee532f16b3bf239ca2c2538d1373efe7","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:27:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f08f3df72a7490f5dd5914fcabcb521fd85d4b1b","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:30:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a82fae43d0c5e00c98a9d128fb8b925135904a","tid":1459963,"uid":79513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:33:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a66c46220dad44c7de6ea0c37f3881026a49d524","tid":1459963,"uid":185022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c41233d5a8b28126b6d5c7999a6cf6f70d6685","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:44:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d03931f95c5d8885d1c799c9f48545fba91a6ce","tid":1459963,"uid":4948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AhX7DNQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAhX7DNQ.png&h=83ce5d08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64402d4837184f0cbb006fa652ec652fbe4763ff","tid":1459963,"uid":158523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:48:20.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"db9225f038b78c13b90bdb0073a2c9227068f736","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:57:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17aac313e789f9737c14177f024f8a2d591f7950","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:05:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7050f66615f077c8e08e905a4341bcb2bfa71d47","tid":1459963,"uid":9103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:28:06.000Z","msg":"叫人走無問題<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但屌人地唔走 話人係鬼同送頭就大問題呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"5d0daf12b1fd66ae4d45ec2eccecc5b14ea1205a","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:23:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e53663f9b6a73d7d4c832232caff69fb71846e81","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7050f66615f077c8e08e905a4341bcb2bfa71d47","tid":1459963,"uid":9103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:28:06.000Z","msg":"叫人走無問題<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但屌人地唔走 話人係鬼同送頭就大問題呀</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:23:54.000Z","msg":"無錯 所以岩唔岩都好唔好互屌"},{"pid":"62968fa7aa08cd10db77ccc841a78231a4e281a5","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:48:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a87a29ce748345c5047e1384d0b569065b04db11","tid":1459963,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:51:51.000Z","msg":"陳雲：（接續策略帖文）我們暫停衝擊的時候，國際社會就找到安全的反應時間做事（safe reaction time-span）。目前港共已經犯下最殘暴也是最明顯的人道罪行&mdash;&mdash;警察開槍射盲女性救護員的眼，我們就在此暫停衝擊行動，轉做和平集會、展覽、宣傳，也請外國領事來監護我們的和平集會。<br />\n這是給予外國政要一個安全的反應時間，令他們可以譴責香港政府的殘暴行為。而因為我們已經暫停武力衝擊或武力抵抗，我們不會犯錯而令這些外國政要尷尬，例如當外國政要譴責香港政府殘暴的時候，我們第二日就在衝擊場所傷殘了一位警察或打死一個黑社會，這會令外國政要非常之尷尬的。<br />\n我是進入了禪定狀態給大家行動意見的。<br />\n玩外交關係，是這樣玩。香港建國之後，我會退出政壇，但我會持續講授這些策略給香港新一代的外交官，玩死中國。"},{"pid":"49025c25ae868c62f0135c960f32d0335e1adf48","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:54:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"602d8b31655fe7223776f38c35757554e563ff09","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:54:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abb9a13008070bbfdc4d9521708aac8f690c4dbd","tid":1459963,"uid":72510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:54:34.000Z","msg":"[置頂] [上線啦!!!] 夢遊機場 Online攻略<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDeeLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDeeLS</a>"},{"pid":"5b43df67f8834ed4527b3d34d1170779a4cc838b","tid":1459963,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:56:24.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"7202a47581dab5b64197ac29e0fde926ba1527a3","tid":1459963,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:59:29.000Z","msg":"我都好嬲，但係我地要贏<br />\n贏左我地就可以慢慢報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc559438477e1e744c5c6020fea15471164a08c2","tid":1459963,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"所以你咪俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b290ee36b01cf2c03a4a8759c3704c77177934e","tid":1459963,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf64dbf9df0bd12b2db5f662b93e3b5a9608005","tid":1459963,"uid":245965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:37:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}